0. About

Filer is a simple Perl/Gtk2 based file manager.

1. Dependencies

* File::BaseDir (available on CPAN)

* File::MimeInfo (available on CPAN)

* File::DirWalk (available on CPAN)

* Class::Bind (http://github.com/nullmedium/Class-Bind)

* Gtk2-Perl (http://gtk2-perl.sf.net/)

2. Installation

If you want to install Filer, instead of using it out of the box
in its own directory, you can use the small and straightforward Makefile.

	$ make install

or

	$ make install PREFIX=prefix

depending on your chosen PREFIX, filer will be installed
as ${PREFIX}/bin/filer

You may want to add ${PREFIX}/bin to your PATH
